OL,3,CMore than half of businesses believe
OL,4,Cgovernment strategy hurts growth
OL,6,FJersey business leaders are expressing
OL,7,F"widespread pessimism" about the
OL,8,Fisland's economic outlook and have
OL,9,Fjoined forces to call for targeted
OL,10,Faction from the island's government on
OL,11,Fkey issues.
OL,13,FA Jersey Institute of Directors (IoD)
OL,14,Fsurvey reveals more than half of
OL,15,Fbusinesses view the island's economic
OL,16,Fconditions and government strategy as
OL,17,Fmajor barriers to growth, while 12%
OL,18,Fhave made redundancies in the last 12
OL,19,Fmonths.
