OL,3,CMore than half of businesses believe
OL,4,Cgovernment strategy hurts growth
OL,6,FThe study also lays bare skills
OL,7,Fshortages which have led to vacancies
OL,8,Fin nearly a quarter of organisations.
OL,10,FMany are tightening their budgets with
OL,11,F29% planning to reduce or freeze their
OL,12,Fspending and 26% expecting a decline
OL,13,Fin stable profits.
OL,15,FThe research underlines concerns about
OL,16,Fhow the Government plans to deal with
OL,17,Fthe problems facing businesses
OL,18,Fincluding the high cost of living.
