OL,3,CMore than half of businesses believe
OL,4,Cgovernment strategy hurts growth
OL,6,FDeputy Kirsten Morel, Jersey's
OL,7,FSustainable Economic Development
OL,8,FMinister, says: "We are coming out of
OL,9,FCovid still, we are coming out of
OL,10,FBrexit, and as a result, I think it is
OL,11,Fimportant that we focus and prioritise
OL,12,Fthe economy because you don't get
OL,13,Fhealthcare, you don't get an
OL,14,Feducation, without a strong economy
OL,15,Fbelow them."
OL,17,FWhat are the main areas of concern?
OL,19,FThose who responded to the business
OL,20,Fsurvey highlighted several factors
OL,21,Fthat negatively impact growth:
