OL,6,FIoD Jersey and the Chamber of Commerce
OL,7,Fare coming together to urge the
OL,8,FGovernment to take specific actions
OL,9,Fthat will encourage investment and
OL,10,Frebuild confidence in the economy.
OL,12,FCommenting on the findings, Alex
OL,13,FRuddy, Chair of IoD Jersey says:
OL,14,F"Jersey's business community is
OL,15,Fsending a clear message, economic
OL,16,Funcertainty, government strategy, and
OL,17,Fworkforce pressures are holding back
OL,18,Finvestment and growth.
OL,20,F"Our island needs targeted action to
OL,21,Frestore business confidence."
