OL,6,FMurray Norton, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FJersey's Chamber of Commerce, adds:
OL,8,F"Jersey's business community remains
OL,9,Fresilient despite economic pressures,
OL,10,Fbut confidence is fragile.
OL,12,F"High living costs, labour expenses,
OL,13,Fand skills shortages strain businesses
OL,14,Fand need addressing.
OL,16,F"With the right support, Jersey has
OL,17,Fthe potential for renewed confidence
OL,18,Fand stability."
OL,20,FDeputy Morel adds: "I wasn't surprised
OL,21,Fby anything in the report.
