OL,6,F"Unless we have that strong economy
OL,7,Fwhich I know Jersey can have, we will
OL,8,Frun into a number of problems.
OL,10,F"From being in this job for three
OL,11,Fyears, I understand really well the
OL,12,Fissues that businesses are facing. I
OL,13,Fknow that businesses can withstand
OL,14,Fthem, but we need the Government's
OL,15,Fhelp in different ways.
OL,17,F"There is much better confidence over
OL,18,Fhere than in the UK, that doesn't
OL,19,Fsurprise me, we do have a much
OL,20,Fstronger economy than the UK.
